* Validation\nFailure Actions
** Warn (default)
***_ All records written
***_ Metrics logged
***_ Monitoring & analysis
***_ Establish baselines
** Drop
***_ Invalid records removed
***_ Valid records continue
***_ @dp.expect_or_drop
***_ ON VIOLATION DROP ROW
** Fail
***_ Pipeline stops
***_ Transaction rolls back
***_ @dp.expect_or_fail
***_ Critical data integrity
** Monitoring
***_ Pipeline UI metrics
***_ Data quality tab
***_ Pass/fail rates per expectation
***_ Identify systematic issues
@endmindmap
